---
import Prose from "@components/Prose.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="Now | Hyun Don Moon"
  pageDescription="What I'm up to right now"
>
  <Prose>
    <h1>Now</h1>

    <p>
      This page is inspired by Derek Sivers' <a
        href="https://nownownow.com/about"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">/now pages</a
      > movement. It's a simple concept: a page that tells you what someone is focused
      on at this point in their life.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h3>August, 2025</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Work & Learning</strong>: Studying Vue, Node.js, and bundlers like webpack using the Gemini CLI to grow as a frontend platform engineer, and recently shared a write-up on a URL encoding fix with my colleagues.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Projects</strong>: Automating this "Now" page's updates using n8n and Google Gemini.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Reading</strong>: Finished reading the insightful <em>Dopamine Nation</em> and now enjoying <em>Bad Blood</em> by John Carreyrou.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Gaming</strong>: Got hooked on playing <em>Slay the Spire</em> during my commute.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Personal</strong>: Won a pristine M1 MacBook Pro for just $250 at a company auction!
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:2em; font-size:0.9em; color: #666;">
        This page was updated automatically using n8n & Google Gemini.
      </p>
    </section>
  </Prose>
</BaseLayout>